<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
        <h2 style="color: #27ae60;">Payment Approved!</h2>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Great news! Your payment for booking <strong>{{bookingNumber}}</strong> has been approved.</p>
        <p>Your booking is now <strong>Confirmed</strong>.</p>
        <p>Tour: {{tourTitle}}</p>
        <p>Amount: {{amount}}</p>
        <p>You can view your booking details in your profile.</p>
        <hr>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">TrekStories Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
